🟦 Phase 1 – Project Setup & Infrastructure
Read `migration-plan.md` and `sign-mt-architecture.md` to understand the full context.

Then execute **Phase 1: Project Setup & Infrastructure** only. Do NOT proceed to Phase 2.

Tasks:
- Initialize Spring Boot project using Maven with dependencies:
